title: 'Beautiful deck üòçüòçüòç'
body: 'The media could not be loaded. I am loving these not so big and rectangular shaped cards. The cardstock is surprisingly nice too at this price. The best part is holographic images are looking insanely good and i personally felt connected to these cards. There is so much positivity in these cards i felt love inside my heart space. This has become my favourite version of rider waitte. Some people might not like the two titles written in the bottom though as previous version has english titles at the bottom with chinese titles below it in golden now they have made an english version so there are two titles in major arcana cards and court cards .But trust me the symbolism is as clear as centennial smith tarot even at this size. I am in love. Thankyou so much for great packing and for delivering a beautiful and sturdy deck.'
